# 4. MVP vs Full Version Scope

A clear distinction between what ships in the MVP and what comes later:

| **Feature Area** | **MVP (v1.0)** | **Full Version (v2.0+)** |
| --- | --- | --- |
| **AI Recommendations** | Basic mood + weather + preference-based suggestions | Deep behavioral learning, time-of-day patterns, health integration |
| **Diet Support** | Manual selection: vegetarian, non-veg, calorie range | Pregnancy plans, recovery diets, fitness goals with nutritionist validation |
| **Recipes** | Curated Indian recipe database (500+ recipes) | User-submitted recipes, regional cuisine deep-dive, video tutorials |
| **Ordering** | Deep links to Swiggy/Zomato for the suggested dish | In-app ordering with price comparison across platforms |
| **Groceries** | Ingredient checklist (manual) | One-tap grocery ordering via BigBasket/Blinkit integration |
| **Social** | Not in MVP | Share meals, family groups, meal challenges |
| **Monetization** | Free app with basic features | Premium tier, affiliate revenue, brand partnerships |

# 5. Revenue Model Deep-Dive

## 5.1 Freemium Tier Breakdown

| **Feature** | **Free Tier** | **Premium Tier** |
| --- | --- | --- |
| **Meal Suggestions** | AI-powered daily suggestions | AI-powered daily suggestions |
| **Recipes ****&**** Cooking** | Full recipe access with steps | Full recipe access with steps |
| **Mood/Weather Integration** | Yes | Yes |
| **Order Online Integration** | Yes (deep links) | Yes (deep links) |
| **Ingredient Checklist** | Yes | Yes |
| **Ad-Free Experience** | No (ads supported) | Yes — completely ad-free |
| **Meal Insights ****&**** Analytics** | No | Yes — weekly/monthly meal trends & nutrition summary |
| **Health ****&**** Diet Profiles** | No | Yes — pregnancy, recovery, fitness, calorie goals |
| **Family Profiles** | No | Yes — manage meals for entire family |
| **Smart Ingredient Planning** | No | Yes — pantry tracking + smart grocery lists |

## 5.2 Pricing Strategy

Launch Strategy: The app will be completely FREE for the first 3 months post-launch. During this period, all users get access to the full experience with no restrictions. This builds a strong user base, generates feedback, and creates habit before any monetization begins.

Post Free Period: Premium subscription at ₹99/month or ₹799/year (33% savings on annual). The core meal suggestion experience remains free forever — premium unlocks the five advanced features listed above. This positions the app below most food delivery subscriptions while offering daily value.

# 6. Budget Allocation (₹50K – ₹1L)

With a tight budget and AI-assisted development, here’s how to allocate funds strategically:

| **Category** | **Estimated Cost** | **Notes** |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Apple Developer Account | ₹8,700/year | Required for iOS App Store |
| Google Play Developer | ₹2,100 (one-time) | Required for Play Store |
| Domain + Hosting | ₹2,000 – 3,000/year | Landing page, API hosting |
| Cloud Services (Free Tier) | ₹0 initially | AWS/GCP/Firebase free tiers |
| AI API Credits | ₹5,000 – 10,000 | OpenAI/Gemini for MVP testing |
| AI Coding Tools | ₹5,000 – 10,000 | Claude Pro, Cursor Pro, etc. |
| UI/UX Design Tools | ₹0 – 2,000 | Figma (free tier), Canva |
| Marketing (Launch) | ₹10,000 – 20,000 | Social media, influencer seeding |
| Miscellaneous | ₹5,000 – 10,000 | Buffer for unexpected costs |
| **TOTAL** | **₹37,800 – ₹65,800** | Well within ₹50K–1L budget |

# 7. Key Assumptions & Risks

| **Assumptions** | **Risks ****&**** Mitigations** |
| --- | --- |
| People are willing to let AI decide meals | User resistance to AI suggestions → Allow easy customization and overrides |
| Free tier is compelling enough to drive downloads | Low conversion to premium → Test pricing, add compelling premium-only features |
| Delivery platform APIs are accessible or can be deep-linked | API access denied → Start with deep links, pursue partnerships |
| AI coding tools can build a production-quality app | Code quality risks → Invest in testing, use established frameworks |
| Indian users will pay ₹99/month for meal suggestions | Price sensitivity → Start with longer free trial, test ₹49 tier |
| Recipe database can be bootstrapped with available data | Content quality → Curate manually, partner with food bloggers |

# 8. MVP Success Metrics

These are the numbers that determine if we proceed to full version:

| **Metric** | **Target (3 months)** | **Signal** |
| --- | --- | --- |
| **App Downloads** | **5,000+** | Market interest exists |
| **Daily Active Users** | **500+ DAU** | Product has retention |
| **Suggestion Accept Rate** | **>****40%** | AI recommendations are useful |
| **7-Day Retention** | **>****25%** | Users find ongoing value |
| **Premium Conversion** | **>****3%** | Willingness to pay is real |
| **App Store Rating** | **4.0+ stars** | User satisfaction |
| **NPS Score** | **>****30** | Users would recommend |

